<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Jessica, me too! :) In addition to the Lynch, Kubrick and von Trier suggested below, I&apos;d also suggest Dario Argento&apos;s &apos;Suspiria.&apos; It ends in a silly w<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Jessica, me too! :) In addition to the Lynch, Kubrick and von Trier suggested below, I'd also suggest Dario Argento's 'Suspiria.' It ends in a silly way but up until then it's very eerie, with a nice, creepy score, and amazing visuals/production design.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
